</p>

<pre>
             k[i]
     y[i] = ------ u[i]
              s
</pre>

<p><b>Release Notes:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><i>Nov. 4, 1999</i>
       by <a href=\"http://www.robotic.dlr.de/Martin.Otter/\">Martin Otter</a>:<br>
       Vectorized.</li>
<li><i>June 30, 1999</i>
       by <a href=\"http://www.robotic.dlr.de/Martin.Otter/\">Martin Otter</a>:<br>
       Realized.</li>
</ul>
</HTML>
