the output y=outPort.signal element-wise as <i>PI</i> system:
</p>

<pre>
                        1
   y[i] = k[i] * (1 + ------ ) * u[i]
                      T[i]*s

                 T[i]*s + 1
        = k[i] * ----------- * u[i]
                    T[i]*s
</pre>

<p>
